headline: Conagra’s High Protein Breakfast Bowls Test Support For Frozen Growth Story
summary: Conagra Brands, trading as NYSE:CAG, has introduced new Banquet MEGA Breakfast Bowls to expand its frozen breakfast lineup. The products feature high protein content and a new steaming technology designed to improve texture and taste. This launch targets consumers looking for quick, protein focused breakfast options in the frozen aisle. Conagra Brands is rolling out Banquet MEGA Breakfast Bowls at a time when its share price sits at $19.35. The stock has seen a 14.2% return over the past 30...
